Cyberpunk style: A towering holographic classroom floats above a neon-drenched futuristic Asian cityscape at night, with translucent digital screens displaying mathematical equations and scientific diagrams cascading like waterfalls around it. Below, tiny silhouettes of students with glowing backpacks walk across elevated glass walkways connecting to the floating structure. The classroom itself is a mix of traditional wooden desks merged with chrome and circuitry, half-dissolved into streams of blue and purple data particles. A lone teacher figure stands at the center, their form flickering between solid human and digital avatar, reaching toward students who appear both physically present and as ghostly holograms. Rain falls through laser grid patterns in the sky, reflecting off wet surfaces in electric pink and teal. The mood captures uncertainty and transformation—the old world of education literally dissolving into something new and unknown.
